{
  "texts": [
    "We demonstrated ATLA's effectiveness through extensive analyses and empirical results.",
    "However, ATLA has two limitations.",
    "First, ATLA experiences approximation errors related to the two objectives: L e and L s.",
    "We have thoroughly examined the proxy properties of the two objectives in App.C and E. Second, the generated harmful responses tend to follow a rigid format.",
    "This limitation is discussed in App.J, supported with empirical observations."
  ]
}